Viva Questions

What is a Git Repository?

A storage location that tracks files and their changes.

What is a Commit?

A snapshot of project changes.

Command to view compact history?

git log --oneline

Difference between Revert and Reset?

Revert creates a new commit to undo changes, while Reset removes commits from history.

Command to check branch?

git branch

Command to check repository status?

git status

